{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "54806a43-8333-4b9d-aa0d-c2de5725f5f5",
    "name": "UTS Web Service API",
    "description": "# UTS Web Service API\nDokumentasi Postman untuk project Laravel Web Service.\n\n## Base URL\n- Web: `{{base_url}}`\n- API: `{{api_url}}`\n\n## Authentication\nProject ini menggunakan Laravel session + CSRF untuk login web, bukan JWT. Setelah login, gunakan cookie session yang sama untuk request API yang memerlukan autentikasi.\n\n## Catatan\n- Request public: books read, categories read, Groq test.\n- Request protected: login session, loans, AI, create/update/delete books, create/update/delete categories.\n- Gunakan `Save as Example` di Postman untuk menyimpan contoh response sukses dan error.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8000" },
    { "key": "api_url", "value": "{{base_url}}/api" },
    { "key": "csrf_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "book_id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "loan_id", "value": "1" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01 Authentication",
      "description": "## Folder Authentication\n`STATUS: PRODUCTION` untuk login web berbasis session.\n\nGunakan endpoint ini untuk mendapatkan cookie session sebelum akses ke endpoint protected.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Login Page",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "text/html" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/login"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "html",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "text/html; charset=utf-8" }],
              "body": "<html>\n  <head>\n    <title>Laravel</title>\n    <meta name=\"csrf-token\" content=\"...\">\n  </head>\n  <body>Login page</body>\n</html>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Session",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "text/html,application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                { "key": "email", "value": "admin@gmail.com", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "password", "value": "password", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "_token", "value": "{{csrf_token}}", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/login"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "302 Redirect",
              "status": "Found",
              "code": 302,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "html",
              "header": [{ "key": "Location", "value": "{{base_url}}/dashboard" }],
              "body": "<html>\n  <head>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"refresh\" content=\"0;url='{{base_url}}/dashboard'\" />\n  </head>\n  <body>Redirecting to dashboard</body>\n</html>"
            },
            {
              "name": "419 CSRF Error",
              "status": "Page Expired",
              "code": 419,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "html",
              "body": "<html>\n  <head><title>Page Expired</title></head>\n  <body>CSRF token mismatch</body>\n</html>"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 Invalid Credentials",
              "status": "Unprocessable Entity",
              "code": 422,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"These credentials do not match our records.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "text/html,application/json" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "urlencoded", "urlencoded": [{ "key": "_token", "value": "{{csrf_token}}", "type": "text" }] },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/logout"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "302 Redirect",
              "status": "Found",
              "code": 302,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "html",
              "header": [{ "key": "Location", "value": "{{base_url}}/login" }],
              "body": "<html><body>Redirecting to login</body></html>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Authenticated User",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{api_url}}/user"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"name\": \"Admin\",\n  \"email\": \"admin@gmail.com\",\n  \"role\": \"admin\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "401 Unauthorized",
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Unauthenticated.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "02 Books",
      "description": "## Folder Books\n`STATUS: PRODUCTION`\n\nEndpoint buku publik untuk baca data, serta endpoint admin untuk create, update, dan delete.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get All Books",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }], "url": "{{api_url}}/books" },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"current_page\": 1,\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Est eos quia est.\",\n      \"author\": \"Josefa Thiel\",\n      \"category\": \"Romance\",\n      \"published_year\": 1992,\n      \"isbn\": \"9794596121140\",\n      \"image\": null,\n      \"stock\": 26\n    }\n  ],\n  \"per_page\": 15,\n  \"total\": 100\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Book Detail",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }], "url": "{{api_url}}/books/:id" },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"title\": \"Est eos quia est.\",\n  \"author\": \"Josefa Thiel\",\n  \"description\": \"Aperiam et perspiciatis consequuntur voluptas...\",\n  \"category\": \"Romance\",\n  \"published_year\": 1992,\n  \"isbn\": \"9794596121140\",\n  \"image\": null,\n  \"stock\": 26\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "404 Not Found",
              "status": "Not Found",
              "code": 404,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"No query results for model [App\\\\Models\\\\Book] 999999\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Book Recommendations",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }], "url": "{{api_url}}/books/recommend?query=Fiction" },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"content\": \"1. Est eos quia est. - romance yang ringan\\n2. Facere enim. - cocok untuk teknologi\",\n  \"usage\": {\n    \"total_tokens\": 215,\n    \"completion_time\": 0.15\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Book",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "title", "value": "Buku Baru", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "author", "value": "Penulis Baru", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "description", "value": "Deskripsi buku baru", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "category", "value": "Fiction", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "published_year", "value": "2026", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "isbn", "value": "9781234567890", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "stock", "value": "3", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "image", "type": "file", "src": "" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{api_url}}/books"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "201 Created",
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": 101,\n  \"title\": \"Buku Baru\",\n  \"author\": \"Penulis Baru\",\n  \"category\": \"Fiction\",\n  \"published_year\": 2026,\n  \"isbn\": \"9781234567890\",\n  \"stock\": 3\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 Validation Error",
              "status": "Unprocessable Entity",
              "code": 422,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"errors\": {\n    \"title\": [\"The title field is required.\"]\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Book",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Buku Baru Update\",\n  \"stock\": 5\n}" },
            "url": "{{api_url}}/books/:id"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"title\": \"Buku Baru Update\",\n  \"stock\": 5\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Book",
          "request": { "method": "DELETE", "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }], "url": "{{api_url}}/books/:id" },
          "response": [
            { "name": "200 OK", "status": "OK", "code": 200, "_postman_previewlanguage": "json", "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Book deleted\"\n}" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
